    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a smooth, worry-free experience on the road. It\u2019s clean, runs beautifully, and is just waiting for its next adventure! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
