    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its distinct individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive layout is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior mechanical grip. This example maintains its structural rigidity and features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage the McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive throttle actuator service and a fresh fluid flush. While showing signs of spirited road use, the chassis remains balanced and the atmospheric induction provides a linear power delivery that modern forced-induction units cannot replicate.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
