    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that offers a fantastic blend of reliability and comfort. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. The interior is in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, operates exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, reflecting a consistent maintenance history. We recently performed a full fluid flush and replaced the air filters. The tires are at approximately 70% tread, providing excellent grip and a quiet ride. This car has been kept in a smoke-free environment and has primarily been used for commuting. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and is ready to provide its next owner with many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
