    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin. I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
