    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure mechanical longevity, the double-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical upgrade for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear arrangement for precise turn-in and cornering stability. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains in excellent health, exhibiting a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This is a driver-focused machine with sorted mechanicals ready for the enthusiast who values performance over a concours finish.",
